{"total":55,"pageSize":12,"pageCount":5,"data":[{"title":"第一次深度学习尝试","uid":"b0401276265368b4880a947fdf74a498","slug":"第一次深度学习尝试","date":"2021-11-21T14:17:08.000Z","updated":"2022-03-29T06:36:51.823Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/第一次深度学习尝试.json","cover":["https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/DEEPLEARN.jpg"],"text":"信息论小组作业，我主要负责代码部分。搭建起深度学习的环境，并把程序运行起来。 这是我第一次使用python进行深度学习，深度学习与人工智能是我一直以来都很感兴趣的方向，也是我未来意向从事的方向。 但是目前我对于深度学习所了解的东西太少了，本科期间的培养方案上也没有相关的课程，感觉...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"33k","symbolsTime":"30 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"深度学习","slug":"深度学习","count":2,"path":"api/categories/深度学习.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"Python","slug":"Python","count":8,"path":"api/tags/Python.json"},{"name":"深度学习","slug":"深度学习","count":3,"path":"api/tags/深度学习.json"},{"name":"PyTorch","slug":"PyTorch","count":1,"path":"api/tags/PyTorch.json"},{"name":"WSL","slug":"WSL","count":1,"path":"api/tags/WSL.json"}],"author":{"name":"Murphy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/aboutme.jpg","link":"/","description":"A Future Without Disappointment!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/murphyhoucn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/CosmicDusty","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/img/bilibili.png","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/294812632"}}}},"feature":false},{"title":"ESP32CAM","uid":"32677db4598a540c2b555119b6c942b8","slug":"ESP32CAM","date":"2021-10-14T14:16:52.000Z","updated":"2022-03-29T06:36:52.167Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ESP32CAM.json","cover":["https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/esp32cam.jpg"],"text":"ESP32-CAM是安信可最新发布小尺寸的摄像头模组。该模块可以作为最小系统独立工作，尺寸仅为2740.54.5mm，深度睡眠电流最低达到6mA。ESP32-CAM可广泛应用于各种物联网场合，适用于家庭智能设备、工业无线控制、无线监控、QR无线识别，无线定位系统信号以及其它物联网...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":700,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"电子电路","slug":"电子电路","co