jing.aliyuncs.com/website/esp32.jpg"],"text":"ESP32模块是ESP8266的升级版本。除了Wi-Fi模块，该模块还包含蓝牙4.0模块。双核CPU工作频率为80至240 MHz，包含两个Wi-Fi和蓝牙模块以及各种输入和输出引脚， ESP32是物联网项目的理想选择。 ","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":115,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"电子电路","slug":"电子电路","count":5,"path":"api/categories/电子电路.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"单片机","slug":"单片机","count":4,"path":"api/tags/单片机.json"}],"author":{"name":"Murphy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/aboutme.jpg","link":"/","description":"A Future Without Disappointment!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/murphyhoucn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/CosmicDusty","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/img/bilibili.png","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/294812632"}}}},"feature":false},{"title":"ArduinoUno","uid":"0892a559d6416c59f72bd85df6acf532","slug":"ArduinoUno","date":"2021-10-10T14:16:31.000Z","updated":"2022-03-29T06:36:52.167Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/ArduinoUno.json","cover":["https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/arduinouno.png"],"text":"Arduino是一款便捷灵活、方便上手的开源电子原型平台。包含硬件（各种型号的Arduino板）和软件（ArduinoIDE）。由一个欧洲开发团队于2005年冬季开发。其成员包括Massimo Banzi、David Cuartielles、Tom Igoe、Gianluca M...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":304,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"电子电路","slug":"电子电路","count":5,"path":"api/categories/电子电路.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"单片机","slug":"单片机","count":4,"path":"api/tags/单片机.json"}],"author":{"name":"Murphy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/aboutme.jpg","link":"/","description":"A Future Without Disappointment!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/murphyhoucn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/CosmicDusty","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/img/bilibili.png","link