习记录","slug":"学习记录","count":8,"path":"api/tags/学习记录.json"}],"author":{"name":"Murphy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/aboutme.jpg","link":"/","description":"A Future Without Disappointment!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/murphyhoucn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/CosmicDusty","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/img/bilibili.png","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/294812632"}}}},"feature":false},{"title":"信号与系统","uid":"ce7d6dc94310cffb7a2e474e73ba4156","slug":"信号与系统","date":"2021-09-19T15:59:37.000Z","updated":"2022-03-29T06:36:52.167Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/信号与系统.json","cover":["https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/信号与系统.jpg"],"text":"信号与系统是很重要的一门课，是很多学校通信考研的专业课！这门课几乎每个知识点都很重要，最重要的是三大变换：傅里叶变换，拉普拉斯变换，Z变换。 学好这门课在课本理解和做题两方面都需要抓紧！ 信号与系统在我学的科目中属于做题比较多的了，我自我感觉，对于定义的理解和对于基本题型的解答都...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.2k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"通信工程","slug":"通信工程","count":9,"path":"api/categories/通信工程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"课本学习记录","slug":"课本学习记录","count":5,"path":"api/tags/课本学习记录.json"}],"author":{"name":"Murphy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/aboutme.jpg","link":"/","description":"A Future Without Disappointment!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/murphyhoucn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/CosmicDusty","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/img/bilibili.png","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/294812632"}}}},"feature":false},{"title":"电磁场与电磁波","uid":"0d4afbe80c23cb135c00b07872f2eaf1","slug":"电磁场与电磁波","date":"2021-09-19T14:07:00.000Z","updated":"2022-03-29T06:36:51.823Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/电磁场与电磁波.json","cover":["https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/maxwell.png"],"text":"电磁场与电磁波，这门课有点难，难就难在太多公式了！前半部分是电磁场部分，与大学物理所学的东西有很多重合的地方，因此老师在讲课的时候，回默认大家的大学物理电磁场学的很好，我的大学物理学的并不好，因此电磁场部分学的很吃力，很多知识点都听不太懂，记不住！后半部分是电磁场部分，知识点不多...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"6.3k","symbolsTime":"6 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"通信工程","slug":"通信工程","count":9,"path":"api/categories/通信工程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"课本学习记录","slug":"课本学习记录","count":5,"path":"api/tags/课本学习记录.json"}],"author":{"name":"Murphy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/aboutme.jpg","link":"/","description":"A Future Without Disappointment!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/murphyhoucn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/CosmicDusty","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/img/bilibili.png","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/294812632"}}}},"feature":false},{"title":"信息论基础","uid":"170ac0ec2dd22118a04a0e76ec2166da","slug":"信息论基础","date":"2021-09-19T14:06:52.000Z","updated":"2022-03-29T06:36:52.167Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/信息论基础.json","cover":["https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/信息论.jpg"],"text":"信息论基础与编码，大多数都是讲的信息论基础，编码部分讲的比较少！知识架构就是香农的三大定律：无失真信源编码有噪信道编码限时真信源编码 这门课学的过程很痛苦，太多定义了，到期末的时候完全不懂，即使已经复习完了前四章的知识点，但是对基本的定义都没有掌握，因此复习到第四章感觉效果很差，...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"3.2k","symbolsTime":"3 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"通信工程","slug":"通信工程","count":9,"path":"api/categories/通信工程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"课本学习记录","slug":"课本学习记录","count":5,"path":"api/tags/课本学习记录.json"}],"author":{"name":"Murphy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/aboutme.jpg","link":"/","description":"A Future Without Disappointment!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/murphyhoucn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/CosmicDusty","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/img/bilibili.png","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/294812632"}}}},"feature":false},{"title":"通信电子电路","uid":"2958b4d237c4ef391a037f33406866eb","slug":"通信电子电路","date":"2021-09-19T14:06:45.000Z","updated":"2022-03-29T06:36:51.823Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/通信电子电路.json","cover":["https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/通信电子电路.jpg"],"text":"通信电子电路就是模电的升级版，信号从模电的低频变成了高频，研究的数学原理从线性变成了非线性。这么课是前后关系联系比较紧密的，前面的知识点需要充分的理解，在学习后面知识点时，才能更快速的跟上老师的思路。 第一章 绪论 1.1 通信系统的概念 信息源 发送设备 信道（噪声源） 接收设...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.6k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"通信工程","slug":"通信工程","count":9,"path":"api/categories/通信工程.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"课本学习记录","slug":"课本学习记录","count":5,"path":"api/tags/课本学习记录.json"}],"author":{"name":"Murphy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/img/aboutme.jpg","link":"/","description":"A Future Without Disappointment!","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/murphyhoucn","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"https://www.zhihu.com/people/CosmicDusty","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{"bilibili":{"icon":"/img/bilibili.png","link":"https://space.bilibili.com/294812632"}}}},"feature":false},{"title":"《鸟哥的Linux私房菜》","uid":"91ca453a5f79dd5e7d7cffefd5194251","slug":"《鸟哥的Linux私房菜》","date":"2021-08-01T13:53:25.000Z","updated":"2022-03-29T06:37:23.949Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/《鸟哥的Linux私房菜》.json","cover":["https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/website/CentOS封面.jpg"],"text":"一直以来都对Linux操作系统很感兴趣，林纳斯·本纳第克特·托瓦兹是我很崇拜的一个人。很早就知道了在未来工作当中可能大多数开发都会在Linux操作系统上，于是买了鸟哥的这本书，照着书开始学习Linux。因为鸟哥的书是依据CentOS发行版的，因此我对Linux的学习也将从Cent...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"19k","symbolsTime":"17 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"知识扩展","slug":"知识扩展","count":10,"path":"api/categories/知识扩展.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"操作系统","slug":"操作系统","count":2,"path":"api/tags/操作系统.json"}],"author":{"name":"Murphy","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://murhyimgur.oss-cn-b